  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will investigate the influencing factors of exercise adherence of home-based&#xD;
      cardiac rehabilitation in patients with coronary artery disease.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study will conduct a quantitative questionnaire survey. Patients with coronary artery&#xD;
      disease in home-based cardiac rehabilitation will receive investigation of the influencing&#xD;
      factors of exercise adherence.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
